actions/gameAction.js文件代码
```javascript
import * as TYPES from "../actionType"
export function one(list){ //想要外部调用的方法，需要导出,list为调用时传参
    return (dispatch)=>{
        //这里可以做请求，请求完成后dispatch()调用方法
        // fetch(url+'/user/info/tourist',{
        //     method:'GET',
        //     headers:list
        // }).then(function(response) {
        //     return response.json();
        // })
        // .then(function(myJson) {
        //     console.log("游客信息",myJson)
        //     if(myJson.msg){//获取游客信息失败
        //         alert(myJson.msg)
        //     }else{//登陆成功
        //         dispatch(success(myJson));//存储游客信息
        //     }
        // }).catch(function(error){
        //     alert("请求游客信息失败")
        // })
        dispatch(getOne(list))
    }
}
function getOne(list){
    return{
        type: TYPES.GAME_ACTION_ONE,//这里与actionType里呼应
        one:list
    }
}
export function getTwo(list){
    return{
        type: TYPES.GAME_ACTION_TWO,
        one:list
    }
}
//........很多方法
//说明：Action.js内部方法可以用dispatch()互相调用
```
reducers/gameReducer.js文件代码
```javascript
import * as TYPES from "../../actions/actionType"
/**
 * 这里可以初始化一个默认的实体类
 */
const initialState = {
    //这里就是store里存储的初始值，可以是对象，可以是数组
    aaa:{   
        One:0
    } 
}
export default function getGame(state=initialState,action){
    switch(action.type){
        case TYPES.GAME_ACTION_ONE: //这里与actionType里呼应
            return Object.assign({},state,{
                aaa:{
                    One:action.one //这里与gameAction里传过来的参数呼应
                }
            })
            break
        case TYPES.GAME_ACTION_TWO:
            return Object.assign({},state,{
                aaa:{
                    One:action.one
                }
            })
            break
        default:
            return state;
    }
}
```
reducer文件与action文件都写好了，接下来写把他们关联起来的文件actionType.js(actions文件夹下)
```javascript
//home页面
export const HOME_ACTION_ONE='home_action_one'

//game页面
export const GAME_ACTION_ONE='game_action_one'
export const GAME_ACTION_TWO='game_action_two'
```
> 注意，所有涉及修改store初始值的方法都必须在action里申明，在redux里接收和修改，在actionType里，用type使两文件关联

最后，把所有页面的reducer在reducers.js里导出（reducers文件夹下）
```javascript
import { combineReducers } from 'redux';
// import GetHome from './reducers/home/homeReducer';
import GetGame from "./game/gameReducer"

//这里面必须要有初始数据 - 否则报错
const rootReducer = combineReducers({
    // GetHome,
    GetGame,
});

export default rootReducer;
```

再把store导出在store.js里
```javascript
import {createStore, applyMiddleware} from 'redux';
import thunkMiddleware from 'redux-thunk';
//把reducer引入
import rootReducer from './reducers/reducers'

const store = createStore(rootReducer,applyMiddleware(thunkMiddleware))

export default store;

```



接下来在App.js里引用
```javascript
import React,{Component} from 'react';
import { StyleSheet,View,Text } from 'react-native';

import { Provider } from 'react-redux';
import store from './src/store'//引入stroe

import Game from './src/page/game/game'

export default class App extends Component {
  render(){
    return (
      <Provider store={store}>
          <Game/>
      </Provider>
    )
  }
};
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
});
```

修改page文件夹下，game.js
```javascript
import React,{Component}from 'react';
import {Button,View, Text } from 'react-native';
import { connect } from 'react-redux'

//接收 在gameAction里用export导出的方法
import {one,getTwo} from "../../actions/game/gameAction"

class HomeScreen extends Component {
    componentWillMount(){
        console.log(this.props.GetGame.aaa.One)
        //this.props.GetGame方法，只能读取数据，无法修改
    }
    addOne=()=>{
        this.props.dispatch(one(this.props.GetGame.aaa.One+1))
    }
    setOne(){
        this.props.dispatch(getTwo(0))
    }
    render() {
        return (
            <View style={{ flex: 1, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                <Text>现在One值为：{this.props.GetGame.aaa.One}</Text>
                <Button title="One值加1" onPress={this.addOne}></Button>
                <Button title="设置One值" onPress={this.setOne.bind(this)}></Button>
            </View>
        );
    }
};

//所有需要用到store状态管理的组件都可以引入，引入方法相同
function select(store) {
    return {
        GetGame : store.GetGame,
    //this.props调用方法:reducers.js导出方法
    }
}
export default connect(select)(HomeScreen);
```

<summary>

安装react-navigation依赖
```
yarn add react-native-reanimated react-native-gesture-handler react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context
```


要完成react-native-screensAndroid的安装，请将以下两行添加到中的dependencies部分android/app/build.gradle:
```javascript
implementation project(':react-native-safe-area-context')
implementation project(':react-native-screens')
implementation project(':react-native-gesture-handler')
implementation project(':react-native-reanimated')
implementation fileTree(dir: "libs", include: ["*.jar"])
implementation "com.facebook.react:react-native:+"  // From node_modules
+ implementation 'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.1.0-rc01'
+ implementation 'androidx.swiperefreshlayout:swiperefreshlayout:1.1.0-alpha02'
```
要完成react-native-gesture-handlerAndroid的安装，请对进行以下修改android/app/src/main/java文件夹下MainActivity.java：
```javascript
package com.reactnavigation.example;

import com.facebook.react.ReactActivity;
+ import com.facebook.react.ReactActivityDelegate;
+ import com.facebook.react.ReactRootView;
+ import com.swmansion.gesturehandler.react.RNGestureHandlerEnabledRootView;

public class MainActivity extends ReactActivity {

  @Override
  protected String getMainComponentName() {
    return "Example";
  }

+  @Override
+  protected ReactActivityDelegate createReactActivityDelegate() {
+    return new ReactActivityDelegate(this, getMainComponentName()) {
+      @Override
+      protected ReactRootView createRootView() {
+       return new RNGestureHandlerEnabledRootView(MainActivity.this);
+      }
+    };
+  }
}
```
安装 react-navigation-stack
```
yarn add react-navigation-stack @react-native-community/masked-view
```

```javascript
import React,{Component}from 'react';
import {Button,View, Text } from 'react-native';
import { connect } from 'react-redux'
//接收 在gameAction里用export导出的方法
import {one,getTwo} from "../../actions/game/gameAction"

class HomeScreen extends Component {
    static navigationOptions = {//新增navigation
        title: 'Home',//这里可以设置单独导航栏配置
    };
    componentWillMount(){
        console.log(this.props.GetGame.aaa.One)
        //this.props.GetGame方法，只能读取数据，无法修改
    }
    addOne=()=>{
        this.props.dispatch(one(this.props.GetGame.aaa.One+1))
    }
    setOne(){
        this.props.dispatch(getTwo(0))
    }
    render() {
        return (
            <View style={{ flex: 1, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center'}}>
                <Text>现在One值为：{this.props.GetGame.aaa.One}</Text>
                <Button title="One值加1" onPress={this.addOne}></Button>
                <Button title="设置One值" onPress={this.setOne.bind(this)}></Button>
            </View>
        );
    }
};

//所有需要用到store状态管理的组件都可以引入，引入方法相同
function select(store) {
    return {
        GetGame : store.GetGame,
    //this.props调用方法:reducers.js导出方法
    }
}
export default connect(select)(HomeScreen);
```

新建并修改src/root.js(注册所有页面，统一管理)
```javascript
import { createAppContainer } from 'react-navigation';
import { createStackNavigator } from 'react-navigation-stack';

//引入模块
// import Home from './page/home/home';
import Game from './page/game/game';

// 注册所有的页面
const AppNavigator = createStackNavigator(
    {
        Home:  Game,
        // Details: Home,
    },
    {
        headerMode:"none",//不显示导航栏
        initialRouteName: 'Home',//设置首页路由
        /* 如果需要导航栏，样式可以在这里设置，具体设置请查阅react-navigation文档 */
		// 这里可以设置所有导航栏样式

    }
  );

export default AppContainer = createAppContainer(AppNavigator)
```

修改App.js
```javascript
import React,{Component} from 'react';
```
